)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-Ngh%E1%BB%8B/Ph%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u-ph%C3%BA/poem-PQzTfrS5OJf1tbdTG2885Q">Phục điểu phú - 鵩鳥賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-Ngh%E1%BB%8B/author-P4_Isc8PaPS-90054lCyPA">Giả Nghị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-T%C4%A9nh/Tam-%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-s%C6%A1n/poem-8vgQ7q-vo6tfSsMEVIjVcA">Tam Điệp sơn - 三疊山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-T%C4%A9nh/author-QsXB3NJ2bDAOYiQOgeyy4w">Nguyễn Văn Tĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C3%BD-b%C3%A1t-b%C3%AD-th%C6%B0-bi%E1%BB%87t-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-GjoOrN8-c_Bl_LZTuan6vw">Tặng Lý bát bí thư biệt tam thập vận - 贈李八祕書別三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Th%E1%BA%A5m-vi%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ch%E1%BB%89-t%E1%BB%ADu-gi%E1%BB%9Bi-t%E1%BB%ADu-b%C3%B4i-s%E1%BB%AD-v%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%ADn/poem-qUFS7tVdXZTp3lXaksegwA">Thấm viên xuân - Tương chỉ tửu, giới tửu bôi sử vật cận - 沁園春-將止酒，戒酒杯使勿近</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br></div>	</div>
